        "body": "<p>Set contents of an existing table row with:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>int row;\n....\n// make sure row is set to index of the table row\n// you want to populate\nfor (int c=0; c&lt;values.length; ++c)\n    detail.setValueAt(values[c], row, c);\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p><code>TableModel<\/code> also has <code>setValueAt<\/code> method, if you prefer.<\/p>\n",
